OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,FA note allegedly written by Jeffrey
OL,7,FEpstein before his first suspected
OL,8,Fsuicide attempt has been made public
OL,9,Fby a judge for the first time.
OL,11,FThe short letter was found by
OL,12,FEpstein's former cellmate Nicholas
OL,13,FTartaglione after the billionaire
OL,14,Fpaedophile seemingly tried to take his
OL,15,Fown life on July 23, 2019 - three
OL,16,Fweeks before he died.
OL,18,F"They investigated me for month -
OL,19,Ffound nothing!!!" the note reads.
OL,26,@{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
