FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,F"It is a treat to be able to choose
OL,7,Fone's time to say goodbye. Watcha want
OL,8,Fme to do -Bust out cryin!!
OL,10,F"NO FUN - NOT WORTH IT!!"
OL,12,FTartaglione claimed he discovered the
OL,13,Fpiece of paper inside a book four days
OL,14,Fafter Epstein was found on the floor
OL,15,Fof their cell breathing heavily but
OL,16,Fresponsive.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
