PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,FJudge Kenneth Karas ordered the note's
OL,7,Frelease following a petition from The
OL,8,FNew York Times to the US District
OL,9,FCourt for the Southern District of New
OL,10,FYork.
OL,12,FThe note has not been authenticated,
OL,13,Fand it wasn't mentioned in government
OL,14,Freports examining the circumstances of
OL,15,FEpstein's death, nor did it surface in
OL,16,Fthe Justice Department's recent
OL,17,Frelease of files on the late financier.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
