PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,FThe phrase "Watcha want me to do -
OL,7,FBust out cryin" is an apparent
OL,8,Freference to a 1931 Little Rascals
OL,9,Fshort film, and has been used by
OL,10,FEpstein before in emails released by
OL,11,Fthe US Department of Justice.
OL,13,FEpstein responded to his brother with
OL,14,Fthe phrase in a 2016 email when he was
OL,15,Fnotified his cousin had become a
OL,16,Fgrandfather, and wrote the same to his
OL,17,Fchildhood friend Terry Kafka in 2017.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
