PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,FThe words "No fun!!" were also used in
OL,7,Fanother note describing prison
OL,8,Fconditions found in Epstein's cell
OL,9,Fafter he died, according to ITV News'
OL,10,FNorth American partner CNN.
OL,12,FEpstein denied that he had tried to
OL,13,Ftake his own life on July 23, telling
OL,14,Fa prison psychologist that suicide was
OL,15,Fagainst his Jewish religion and that
OL,16,Fhe was a "coward" who didn't like pain.
OL,26,@xD@JOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
