PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,FHe shared a cell with Tartaglione for
OL,7,Ftwo weeks while they both awaited
OL,8,Ftrials; Epstein on sex trafficking
OL,9,Fcharges and Tartaglione on charges of
OL,10,Fkilling four men, including a man he
OL,11,Ftortured and strangled over stolen
OL,12,Fdrug money.
OL,14,FOne officer reported at the time that
OL,15,FEpistein had believed Tartaglione had
OL,16,Ftried to kill him, according to a memo
OL,17,Fincluded in the Justice Department's
OL,18,Ffiles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,FBoth men were interviewed by jail
OL,7,Fpersonnel on July 31, 2019, according
OL,8,Fto jail records, and the note was
OL,9,Fsubmitted as evidence in Tartaglione's
OL,10,Fcriminal case and was placed under
OL,11,Fseal amid a dispute over his legal
OL,12,Frepresentation.
OL,14,FEpstein said he had never had any
OL,15,Fissues with Tartaglione, wasn't
OL,16,Fthreatened by him and didn't "want to
OL,17,Fmake up something that isn't there".
OL,26,@xD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
