PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,FTartaglione denied assaulting Epstein,
OL,7,Fsaid he didn't have any issues being
OL,8,Fhis cellmate, and described thinking
OL,9,Fthe financier was having a heart
OL,10,Fattack on July 23 because his eyes
OL,11,Fwere open and he appeared to be
OL,12,Fsnoring.
OL,14,FPrison officials put Epstein on
OL,15,Fsuicide watch for 31 hours after the
OL,16,Fincident, before downgrading him to
OL,17,Fpsychiatric observation, which was his
OL,18,Fstatus when he died at the
OL,19,FMetropolitan Correctional Center in
OL,20,FManhattan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
