PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778191867
OL,3,C'Suicide note' found in Epstein's cell
OL,4,Cweeks before death is made public
OL,6,FFew people had known about the note's
OL,7,Fexistence until Tartaglione, a former
OL,8,Fpolice officer now serving a life
OL,9,Fsentence, mentioned it last year on
OL,10,Fwriter Jessica Reed Kraus' podcast.
OL,12,FTartaglione, who has appealed his
OL,13,Fconviction, said he gave the note to
OL,14,Fhis lawyers in case Epstein continued
OL,15,Fto claim he had assaulted him.
